      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; k-omega SST turbulence model selection justified by literature precedent for rotating blood pump flows.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST selected based on published benchmarks for centrifugal pump hemolysis CFD (Fraser et al. 2011, Hariharan et al. 2018). Formal model form uncertainty quantification not required at MRL 2."
