      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; nominal input values with documented sources are sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Blood analogue viscosity and density taken from manufacturer datasheet with traceability. Pump geometry from FDA-released CAD file. Input uncertainty propagation not required at MRL 2."
