      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; single-pump-unit experimental data with documented fluid batch is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "PIV and hemolysis bench tests conducted on a single FDA pump unit with one fluid batch. Sample variability assessment not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "factorType": "Equivalency of input parameters",
