      "acceptanceCriteria": "Not assessed at MRL 2; qualitative confirmation that CFD inputs match experimental conditions is sufficient.",
      "rationale": "Qualitative review confirms CFD boundary conditions (flow rate, RPM, fluid properties) match experimental setup within measurement uncertainty. Formal equivalency analysis not required at MRL 2."
